    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight For Survival Against Robots </h2><br>Metal Hunter is a top-down 3D shooter in which you play as a robot that has to fight for his life against other robots. The only way to survive is shooting down all your enemies while dodging the incoming bullets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/cafaa06e2d5b737c492cb5d853587f94.poster.avif?t=1636049944\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/cafaa06e2d5b737c492cb5d853587f94.webm?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/cafaa06e2d5b737c492cb5d853587f94.mp4?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What do you have to do in Metal Hunter? </h2><br><strong>Shoot all your enemies until you are the last one standing</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/8ca1dbff30913af149308d5bd4222d88.poster.avif?t=1636049944\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/8ca1dbff30913af149308d5bd4222d88.webm?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/8ca1dbff30913af149308d5bd4222d88.mp4?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Dodge all the incoming bullets</strong><br>All the bullets in this game are hostile, even yours since they can bounce off walls. Adjust your movement direction so that you are not in the trajectory of any bullets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/d3927737ebae01a3ad7488597b1d86e8.poster.avif?t=1636049944\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/d3927737ebae01a3ad7488597b1d86e8.webm?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/d3927737ebae01a3ad7488597b1d86e8.mp4?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Use your special ability to have better survival chances</strong><br>Your special ability is slowing down time while you and your bullets still move at normal speed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/c6249e9a637c7e129efbd698b3a7445e.poster.avif?t=1636049944\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/c6249e9a637c7e129efbd698b3a7445e.webm?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/c6249e9a637c7e129efbd698b3a7445e.mp4?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Fight Bosses</strong><br>Show off your skills against the bosses you will encounter<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/9a7de76f5a32384e329aaa4ab7940d5e.poster.avif?t=1636049944\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/9a7de76f5a32384e329aaa4ab7940d5e.webm?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/9a7de76f5a32384e329aaa4ab7940d5e.mp4?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Combine your shooting and movement skills to get cool killing steaks</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/8ab298dcd8bf1b7f23266729092e35e7.poster.avif?t=1636049944\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/8ab298dcd8bf1b7f23266729092e35e7.webm?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781520/extras/8ab298dcd8bf1b7f23266729092e35e7.mp4?t=1636049944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is Metal Hunter going to contain at launch?</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Single-player campaign</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Tradeable Items</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Upgrades system</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Character customization</li></ul>",
